TextEng: "I should be going now."
"I want to ask you some questions."
"Tell me about those drow you mentioned."
"It's strange you can't remember what they were looking for."
Text: "그들이 뭘 찾고 있었는지 기억 못 한다니 이상하네."

TextEng: "I'm looking for allies against the Valsharess."
"How did you come to be down here?"
"Better off? How?"
"Tell me about your town."
"I want to know more about this town."
"Tell me where to find the castle."
"Tell me where to find the wizard's tower."
"Tell me where to find the library."
"Tell me where to find the temple."
"Wouldn't you rather live up in the mountains?"
Text: "산 위에서 사는 게 더 낫지 않아?"

TextEng: "Where can I find your Queen?"
"I want to ask you something else."
"Why did she leave the palace?"
"Driders?"
"Serves you right, if you're too dumb to leave."
Text: "당연한 일이지, 떠날 정신도 없을 만큼 멍청하다면."

TextEng: "That's horrible! Why do you stay here?"
"Are you okay? Did something happen to you?"
"Out of my way, unless you want those wings clipped!"
"What are winged elves doing in the Underdark?"
"Beautiful? It's nothing but a cold, damp cave!"
"Is there something you're not telling me?"
"Are you prisoners here?"
"Troubles? Do you mean the drow?"
